data.description: Welcome home!! This house has it all! Wonderful subdivision in a great location! Close to everything but with a country feel. Home offers open concept living and kitchen/dining area with high vaulted ceilings. Appliances to remain. Inside of this home has been freshly painted throughout. Good size bedrooms with a split plan and large master bedroom and bathroom with 2 closets, garden tub and double vanities. Awesome backyard that is fenced with a screened-in porch. 2 car garage is also a plus!
